# ✅ To-Do List Web App

A simple and interactive **To-Do List** web application built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. Users can type in tasks, mark them as complete, and delete them as needed.

## 📸 Preview

![To-Do List Screenshot](#) *(Add screenshot here if needed)*

---

## 🛠️ Features

- ✅ Add new tasks to the list
- ✔️ Mark tasks as completed
- 🗑️ Delete tasks from the list
- 💾 Simple UI using Font Awesome icons
- 💡 Real-time DOM updates with JavaScript

---

## 📂 Project Structure


todo-list-app/
│
├── index.html # Main HTML structure
├── style.css # CSS styles (not provided here)
├── script.js # JavaScript logic
└── README.md # Project documentation


---

## 🔧 How It Works

- **Add Task**: Type in the textarea and click the ✔️ button.
- **Mark Complete**: Click the ✔️ icon next to a task.
- **Delete Task**: Click the 🗑️ icon next to a task.

